OL,4,CHauliers 'must expect Covid test to
OL,5,Center UK'
OL,6, A haulage industry source has said they
OL,7, have been told by the government to
OL,8, expect drivers to have to take a Covid
OL,9, test when coming into the UK from
OL,10, mainland Europe.
OL,12,FThe tests are expected to take place on
OL,13,Fthe UK side.
OL,15,FLorry drivers had previously been
OL,16,Fexempt from testing coming into the UK.
OL,18,FThe Department for Transport said it
OL,19,Fwas "carefully monitoring" an increase
OL,20,Fin cases in Europe and would keep all
OL,21,Fmeasures under review.
